arts.ttl: Myrto Uzuni, Brad Stuver lead Austin to 1-0 victory over St. Louis City
arts.sum: Myrto Uzuni scored his first career goal in the first half and Brad Stuver made it stand up through a one-hour weather delay in the second as Austin FC beat St. Louis City for the first time, 1-0 at Energizer Park on Sunday. Ben Lundt had one save for St. Louis City (2-2-2) in his sixth career start.
